BELMUTH--Harold M., age 78 on January 12, 2007, of Westport, CT and Palm Beach Gardens, FL. Loving husband of Leila, devoted father of Teri Ann Belmuth, Jack Robert Belmuth, Gail Susan Belmuth, father-in-law of Lauri Belmuth & Max Caldwell, brother of Bernice Asher, and adoring grandfather of Cecelia Caldwell, Benjamin Belmuth and Daniel Belmuth. Memorial services Monday Jan 15th at 11:00am from Abraham L. Green and Son Chapel 88 Beach Rd. Fairfield, CT. Memorials to Mid Fairfield Hospice PO Box 489 Wilton, CT 06897
